%h1 Advertising

%p
  Advertising on TorSearch is accomplished by
  =link_to "registering", new_advertiser_registration_path
  or
  =link_to "logging in", new_advertiser_session_path
  , creating an ad, and adding Bitcoin to your account.

%p As soon as the ad is approved by an administrator and your account is funded, your ad will begin to be served.  For each view of your ad, your account will be charged 0.001 BTC, equaling 1,000 pageviews per Bitcoin added to your account.  You can supply more bitcoin to keep your ads showing or you can disable your ads to stop them showing.